Package io.github.eutro.wasm2j.util

Class GraphWalker<T>

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.wasm2j.util.GraphWalker<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of a node in the graph.
public class GraphWalker<T> extends Object
A class for walking a graph depth-first, in pre- or post-order.

    • GraphWalker

      public GraphWalker(T root, F<? super T,? extends Iterable<? extends T>> getChildren)
      Construct a graph walker from a root node and a successor function.

      Elements yielded later by the successor function will be visited first.

      Parameters:
      root - The root of the graph to walk from.
      getChildren - The successor function of the graph.
